{
  "stem": "27390.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted to kill us off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they poisoned the soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'll tell you a little story about soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were on the, on the, on this carriage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It must have been about-- at the end maybe there were about 30 of us left from about 80 or 90.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The rest were dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and there were two guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On each carriage there were two SS guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the SS guards, one-- one evening, it was at night, they got, they gave them soup.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they also had such a container, a soup container.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one of the SS men, he put this container down for a second.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother, he got hold-- he was like a wild animal, my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was worse than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He got hold of this container.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he rushed over to the other end of the carriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And within two seconds, there was nothing left in the container.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I was with him, and we finished off this soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that guard turned around, and he realized the container is gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was going mad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was also starving, hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he started shouting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was looking, whoever pinched his container, he will kill him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he never found who-- he found the container, but it was empty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how it was on that journey.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we-- we-- we drove like this for four weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also back for-- why did it take four weeks?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the lines were bombed all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember one day, we stopped under a bridge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was another carriage, another train was next, on the next, on the next line was another train, an army train with German soldiers running away from the front line.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
